SSLManager

SSL Manager has been designed as a frontend module to generate the required Key and CSR files to order an SSL Certificate then store a copy in a database and email the site admin and user.

INSTALLATION

* Copy sslmanager.cgi and SSLManager.pm to your cgi directory
* Setup your database to store save Key and CSR Data, a Postgresql SQL Dump has been provided. 
  You will need to add the Username and Password details in SSLManager.pm
* Copy the templates folder to your webservers document root.


The following Perl Modules are required. 


